div.h4:
The students have given you a lot of ideas about activities for the exhibition. You would like to organize the ideas in categories, that you can work with.
You have found 6 categories that make sense to you: Workshop, competetions, music and language, role play, digital media and martial arts.
div.h6: Put every activity in the category, that you think is most fitting. Some ideas belong in more categories.
